
  Kirlia    Psychic Type Pokémon

  It is said that a KIRLIA that 
  is exposed to the positive emotions 
  of its TRAINER grows beautiful. 
   Kirlia controls psychokinetic 
  powers with its highly developed 
  brain. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Ralts ► Kirlia ► Gardevoir

 Stage 3 Forms:
  gardevoir
  gallade

